7.text: Kaveen: Ah! That means at 5 o’ clock. Am I right? Hussain: Yes. Earlier the better. Kaveen: That’s true. By the way, how about our meals?

8.text: Hussain: We were asked to bring only breakfast in a lunch box or wrapped in a banana leaf. Lunch will be provided.

10.text: Hussain: Mmm.. an extra uniform, a cap, an umbrella and…urr… a notebook to write down notes when necessary.

12.text: Hussain: Ah, I forgot to tell you. We were all given a booklet each; with details about the places that we’re going to see.

13.text: Kaveen: Oh! How can I get mine?

14.text: Hussain: Don’t worry. I’ve got your copy with me.

15.text: Kaveen: Ok Thanks! I’ll ask my father to get it on his way back home from work. Thank you for calling Hussain. Bye!

16.text: Hussain: Sure. I’ll give it to your father. Let me know the time he’s coming here. See you tomorrow morning. Bye!
